13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 1, Chapter 125, O.S.L.
15 2024 (3 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 501), is amended to read as
16 follows:
17 Section 501. This act shall be known and may be cited as the
18 “Oklahoma Aircraft and Rocket Engine Testing Development Grant
19 Program”.
20 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY Section 2, Chapter 125, O.S.L.
21 2024 (3 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 502), is amended to read as
22 follows:
23 Section 502. A. There is hereby created, within the Oklahoma
24 Department of Aerospace and Aeronautics, the Oklahoma Aircraft and
